<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 11 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1,749.76 on Saturday, up 2.32
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 3,340,736 shares changed hands in 914 deals, and
the turnover was 8.3 billion rials (about 2.76 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
In the trading, shares of 51 companies made gains, and those
of 12 others declined. 
</P>
