<HEADLINE> Beijing's Central Shopping Area Reopens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September (Xinhua) -- The newly remolded Wangfujing
Street, a 700-year-old traditional commercial center in China's
capital, was inaugurated this evening.
</P>
<P>
Nearly one million people gathered in the shopping street to
attend the opening ceremony, and a series of celebratory
activities were held, including the issuing of a souvenir memorial
envelop by the Wangfujing Post Office.
</P>
