<HEADLINE> General Strike Declared in Bangladesh </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, September 12 (Xinhua) -- The combined opposition in
Bangladesh Sunday declared a three-day hartal (general strike)
across the country from Monday to demand the resignation of the
government and immediate parliamentary elections.
</P>
<P>
